features: Get It All Done With Ease: What a smart & pretty way to organize notes, reminders, to do’s and to turn your ideas into actions! The cute spiral notebook set is a fantastic tool for office and home use, for writing down whatever comes to your mind neatly and with style

Plenty Of Space – Set of 3: Perfectly sized at 8.2x6.2” each notebook, an extra double-sided storage pocket for loose notes, documents, grocery lists & more - with ZICOTOs’ college ruled notebook journals set you have everything neatly in one spot

body.description: Ruled College Notebooks Set of 3 by ZICOTO: Your Must-Have Tool For A Well-Organized Home And Professional Life! Thanks to the 8.2x.6.2” note book you are all set to tick off your to do’s, projects and co. with newfound ease. The pages in the notebook are all lined for even & legible writing - super practical! Use the beautiful spiral journaling notebooks to capture spontaneous ideas, to take notes, brainstorm, make to-do lists, map out a marketing strategy or simply for scribbling down anything that comes to your mind. Whether used at home or at the office, the practical notebook set of 3 also provides a wonderful opportunity to let your imagination flow and to unleash your creativity - daydreaming, journaling, doodling - let it all unfold. From a cute, simple notebook to pure magic! Modern Design in beige, saddle, sage green with clever features! Do you want to add loose notes, letters, documents or shopping lists? We’ve got you covered! There are two small storage pockets you can use for additional papers & more. The reliable brass colored spiral binding makes it even easier to organize your tasks. Flipping the pages is a breeze and you can put the notebook down flat without any hassle. As each page has a perforated edge, it is super easy for you to tear-off any page as necessary. The spiral notebook will be your cherished second brain and with its sturdy cover and premium paper it is a durable tool you will never want to miss again.
